Cell["\<\
computeDist is an \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]on the fly\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
function that calculates distances between the 2 atoms to be used in stiff \
ring constraints.
Requires a pdb table and the serial numbers of two atoms in the monomer itp \
file. Outputs the distance. This can be added to a monomer itp file.\
\>", "CodeText",
